{"tid":1987610,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"是咁的.係養和.做咗smile","createTime":"2020-04-24T14:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T02:47:52.000Z","uid":356890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef3009ca7556c31b71c2d65bcc1d60ee963c7ef","tid":1987610,"uid":356890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"雙眼近視5xx ，散光2xx。<br />\n本身都好糾結係清晰定養和做。<br />\n因為大部份朋友都係清晰做。<br />\n但始終相信醫院有保障啲，所以決定係養和做。<br />\n冇指定醫生，張x明醫生 $22000 <br />\n做左三個幾鐘檢查⋯⋯⋯<br />\n因為工作背景關係，醫生覺得我做smile<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會適合啲。<br />\n一開頭我都以為佢會推我去做lasik。<br />\n佢有問我想做邊一樣多啲。<br />\n咁有得俾我揀，梗係揀個傷口細啲。<br />\n～<br />\n手術嗰日，Total有7個人做（4個lasik3個smile）。<br />\n醫生都有Double check+係眼角膜度畫記號。<br />\n然後就入手術室⋯⋯⋯但一見到有六個姑娘就開始有啲驚<br />\n然後姑娘滴最後一次麻醉藥（前後滴咗四次）就準備做手術。<br />\n醫生都會不斷提醒依家開始唔好郁，望實個綠光<br />\n左眼望咗大概10秒到，綠光慢慢冇咗。<br />\n然後我就開始感覺到佢係我既眼上面介左一下咁⋯⋯⋯⋯<br />\n完成之後佢問我有冇感覺 我就答佢 好似冇⋯<br />\n佢就再問多我一次我叫咩名<br />\n然後就做埋右眼，都係做同樣嘅動作。<br />\n手術係成功嘅，但之後第二日覆診見到右眼有一達紅色。<br />\n就問醫生係咪發炎？醫生話琴日右眼郁得比較犀利<br />\n所以佢用左力夾住咗隻眼，所以搞到有瘀血。<br />\nUmmm..嗰刻我以為我冇郁....<br />\n其實做完果一刻都已經有六七成嘅視力<br />\n第二日覆診兩隻眼都係零度近視 但有少少遠視加散光<br />\n（因為本身散光比較深）<br />\n<br />\n一個禮拜之後 左右眼望嘢都係清嘅 但夜晚都係爭啲。<br />\n不過瘀血未散，三個星期之後再覆診。"},{"pid":"acde9f4ca772d8a90c125c39a0b5e5a6d94bbf1c","tid":1987610,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:57:42.000Z","msg":"How much"},{"pid":"159c7e2dcb0c5f263ec8d0a610eefb05b7839953","tid":1987610,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acde9f4ca772d8a90c125c39a0b5e5a6d94bbf1c","tid":1987610,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:57:42.000Z","msg":"How much"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"自膠sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d28a57db8e5b45168f4b3f498793052712672f","tid":1987610,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"而家對眼痛唔痛"},{"pid":"174d6e089374deed65c9369c249b73086bc558cd","tid":1987610,"uid":29080,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"159c7e2dcb0c5f263ec8d0a610eefb05b7839953","tid":1987610,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acde9f4ca772d8a90c125c39a0b5e5a6d94bbf1c","tid":1987610,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:57:42.000Z","msg":"How much"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"自膠sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:59:09.000Z","msg":"真係要去眼科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54716af7a177a5a8bb004cb031362ccad1b150d","tid":1987610,"uid":356890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76d28a57db8e5b45168f4b3f498793052712672f","tid":1987610,"uid":195915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"而家對眼痛唔痛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T15:02:31.000Z","msg":"唔痛呀"},{"pid":"73eaa4baeec9c7e60a3ab8dfa1b011c3f1671375","tid":1987610,"uid":199826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"做緊/做完會唔會痛"},{"pid":"88793f7bce5b805ac84124d282d2a5f7ce4924ce","tid":1987610,"uid":108199,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T17:27:04.000Z","msg":"22000蚊包埋術前檢查見面同咁多次覆診？"},{"pid":"b58e22bb52aa0277e1a3ad07e69e83355be88f94","tid":1987610,"uid":104891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:18:48.000Z","msg":"紅色係爆微血管姐 過幾幾個星期就冇事 睇嘢清就得"},{"pid":"36b1696ce562a8fb376b34117dbf2a83e80093e0","tid":1987610,"uid":13176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T18:23:38.000Z","msg":"呢排疫情期間做？都仲係幾多人下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d83e74c4